name: Defibrillators Def. Defi Defth - Atlanta
description: Screams fall on def ears. Little dogs sic balls. Feet gone. Guts. Your blood pools up. You slide into it like a hot tub, hooking your elbows over the sides so you can reach your Jack 'n Coke. A show of force overcomes your deficits. Resurrections are the definition of small miracles. The game’s on the big screen. Go on and root for your favorite team!
